title: Ryan Hurd & Maren Morris Perform In Studio + Never Gonna Get It + Listener Calls
itunes:title: Ryan Hurd & Maren Morris Perform In Studio + Never Gonna Get It + Listener Calls
description:
Our Friday Morning Conversation this week was with Ryan Hurd & Maren Morris, they stopped by and played a new song for us. We took a bunch of your calls, played a round of Never Gonna Get It, and went over a list of country artists and their cost for a live performance.
